# VectorG Engine JS {{ dimension }}D

**JavaScript and WebAssembly bindings for VectorG Engine.**

This package provides the {{ dimension }}D `@vectorg/{{ js_package_name }}` build of VectorG Engine JS.

VectorG Engine is a real-time vehicle dynamics engine for realistic driving simulation. The bindings target VectorG Engine and are not compatible with upstream Rapier.js.

## Build variants

- standard packages load a separate WebAssembly module;
- `-simd` packages enable WebAssembly SIMD;
- `-deterministic` packages enable cross-platform deterministic simulation; and
- `-compat` packages inline WebAssembly for broader bundler support.

VectorG Engine JS is derived from Rapier.js and Rapier by Dimforge and preserves the original license and attribution.
